<div class="project-text">
    <h3>The Project</h3>
    <p>A Turin tobacconist with a genuine eye for unusual objects decided to build something bigger. The result is a B2B platform supplying a good chunk of northern Italy with the latest in his field. My job was to keep the design vision he had in mind and make it work, adapting and tightening it over time without losing what made it his.</p>
